Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果姐姐隱瞞了什麼 你要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比如在甲州勝沼時 明明援軍不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卻必須命令部下戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤勇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我會跟隨你的 無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為姐姐是唯一的家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,把黑板上的三句話分別分節試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-16\pos(959.785,646.286)}咖哩喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.34,NoticeB,,0,0,0,,{\frz-45\pos(564,837)}吃我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,比較像勇者部的文化祭節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,結城同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是沒什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那能請你讀出現在講到的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,手機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上課時請切斷電源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對不起 停下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧 不是吧 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 大家都怪怪的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 好好聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是… 發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這一天 我們的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,暫時 結束了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明明剛才還在教室裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我又睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,疼 似乎不是在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,畫面變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,總算找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你們兩個都在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸中的萬幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個要是沒有拿著手機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app還有這種功能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,隱藏功能？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個隱藏功能是產生這種情況時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,自動啟動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 好方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app 是入部時風前輩要我們下載的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷靜下來聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是大赦派來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 大赦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,供奉神樹大人的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼特別任務嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明明一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我還是第一次聽說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒被選中 我是打算就這樣瞞過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的班 讚州中學勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,被選中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在看到的這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是神樹大人造出的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼… 不是什麼壞的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是 被神樹大人選中的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,必須在這裡面和敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個點是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幸虧是個慢速的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,浮在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord3\pos(1023,982.5)}Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那是宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了殺死世界而攻過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,殺死世界是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命點的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,到達世界的恩惠 神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候 世界就會死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界裡 只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 是我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,通過大赦的調查 你們被判斷為最有資質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:13.78,Notice,,0,0,0,,全市鄉鎮中學 勇者資質報告書 機密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會… 怎麼可能和那種東西戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,辦法是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要表現出戰鬥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這個app的功能就會解鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,從而成為神樹大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,盯上我們了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已經發現我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥什麼的 不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上東鄉逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,樹也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼能扔下姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我會跟隨你的 無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好 樹 跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是被神樹大人選中的勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是守護這個世界的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,通過神樹大人的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,會把力量借給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,坐雲宵飛車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把手舉起來 表現出戰鬥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎… 出來了什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 連上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,比起擔心我 你那邊沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,數量太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉 抱歉瞞著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩是為大家著想才沒說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一個人沒法挑明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是正符合勇者部的活動目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是風前輩的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 小樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.41,0:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 不要管我 你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼話 怎麼能把朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下朋友不管什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我絕對做不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快逃
