Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,留下痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓大家留下那種回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要努力！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者拳！
